SubString.CExoString: The drow are an evil subrace of elves, living deep underground in the dangerous Underdark.
Your message is inscribed on this paper. You may post it on any bulletin board.
Bound in iron and with a heavy lock, this heavy chest was obviously meant to protect something of value.
